  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI'd like a specialised endpoint to make HTTP requests.\r\nAt the moment the only way to do this is to use `ffi`, but that's not only slow if used intensively, but it also relies on tools like `curl` that are not necessarily present in some environments.\r\n\r\nMy 2 main use cases are:\r\n\r\n- Scripts that can fetch `calldata` from `REST` APIs like 1Inch, Paraswap, etc.\r\n- Tests that can assert things against indexers like `TheGraph`\r\n\r\nRight now I'm using hardhat for each of those things, but I'd like to ditch it as it's slow, it creates a lot of duplication and it's a pain to maintain.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
